This paper deals with reinforcement learning for neural machine translation, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of human feedback for reinforcement learning, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper analyzes the reliability of human feedback, which is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and cybersecurity (cs.CY).
